<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>go on medication • go on the pill</xh5><p> <i>go on medication—</i>start the treatment of an illness using drugs: When these children <u>go on medication</u>, parents are often concerned that daily pill-taking will damage the child’s self-esteem.</p><p> <i>go on the pill—</i>start to take contraceptive pills regularly: Many women who <u>go on the pill</u> have to try out several different brands before they find the right one.</p> </entry>
